<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>결제 실패 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f3ef;
      color: #111;
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    h1 { margin-bottom: 12px; }

    p {
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .info {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 18px;
      background: #fff1ee;
      border-radius: 18px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #b23a2c;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .actions {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    a {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .dark {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .light {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: #111;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>결제에 실패했습니다</h1>
      <p>재고는 차감되지 않았습니다.</p>

      <div class="info">
        <% if (order) { %>
          주문번호: <strong><%= order.merchantUid %></strong><br />
        <% } %>
        실패 사유: <strong><%= reason %></strong>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <a class="dark" href="/order">주문서로 돌아가기</a>
        <a class="light" href="/">메인으로 가기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>